-- POEMS: rune-headed layout forms

=== simple poem | 80
+ a b

=== poem with three children | 80
+ a b c

=== nested poem inline | 80
+ a * b c

=== nested poem chain | 80
+ a * b | c d

=== poem with closed then open | 80
| f | g x

=== poem with bracket child | 80
+ a (b c) d

=== arithmetic style | 80
+ a * b c

=== let binding style | 80
@ x 3 | add x x

=== conditional style | 80
? cond | then | else

=== staircase poems | 80
+ x
- y
* z

=== nested heir poems | 80
~ 1
~ 2
~ 3

=== poem in record | 80
{name : items , value : ~ 1
                        ~ 2
                        ~ 3}

=== poem in tuple | 80
(+ 3 4 , add 3 4 , ? x | add x x)

=== deeply nested poems | 80
@ x 3
| @ y 4
  | add x y

=== readme runic style | 80
= exampleList ~ ? (sillyFn x y)
                | sz | weld [5 -4 3]
                     | map add-x [1 #(x+4 * y)]
              ~ + user : %sol
                + repo : b"plunder"
                + path : /home/sol/r/plunder

=== readme prefix notation | 80
(:= (/ x y) (| if (= y 0) (!! "Error: divide-by-zero")
             (| if (< x y) 0
              (# (+ 1 (/ (- x y) y))))))

=== readme ergonomic rex | 80
:= x/y
 | if y=0 !!"divide-by-zero"
 | if x<y 0
 | #(1 + (x-y / y))
